From: radhevrishi <radhev.232@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 8 May 2026 12:04:23 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 06/17] feat(earnings): concall extraction engine + EDGAR
 small-cap history fallback
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

USER COMPLAINTS:
1. Sector KPIs all showed '○ not extracted' — framework rendered, data
   layer empty. Even with a concall uploaded, nothing scanned it.
2. Concall upload appeared to do nothing — guidance regex ran but no
   visible panel in the report. User couldn't tell anything happened.
3. OSS (One Stop Systems) showed 'No quarterly income statement
   history available from FMP' — small cap not on FMP. The page is
   nearly empty for those tickers despite EDGAR having all the data.

A. CONCALL EXTRACTION ENGINE  (new lib/earnings/india-concall.ts)
   Pure-text, regex-only. No LLM, no network. Returns:
    - topQuotes[4]: sentences ranked by signal density (numbers,
      growth/margin/guidance keywords). Boilerplate / Q&A formalities
      penalised.
    - toneSignals[]: positive / cautious / negative cue phrases drawn
      from a curated phrase table (margin expansion, operating
      leverage, near-term softness, channel destocking, margin
      compression, etc.). Each signal carries the source sentence as
      hover-tooltip context.
    - keyMentions[]: best sentence per topic — operating leverage,
      capex, margins, EPS, new launches, demand environment,
      guidance, input cost / inflation, pricing.
    - sectorKpiHits[]: per-KPI keyword scan (Volume Growth, Rural /
      Urban Mix, Gross Margin, Premiumization, NIM, GNPA, IPM,
      US Generics Pricing, R&D / Sales, etc.). When a KPI matches,
      the row in the Sector KPIs table flips from '○ not extracted'
      to '● mentioned in concall' with the matching sentence shown.
    - Composite Concall Score (0-100) + grade (A+ … F).
      Inputs: sentiment balance × 25%, topic coverage × 25%, KPI
      hits × 25%, top-quote signal density × 25%.

   Wired into india-build.ts via computeIndiaExtras (rawText is
   already plumbed through). Output stashed in indiaExtras.concall
   and surfaced in IndiaInstitutionalReport.tsx as a new 'Concall
   Insights' section between the Quarterly Trend and Working Capital
   panels — only renders when transcript was uploaded.

B. EDGAR HISTORY FALLBACK  (history route)
   Pulls SEC companyfacts JSON when FMP returns empty. Walks the
   us-gaap concept tree for Revenues, GrossProfit, OperatingIncome,
   NetIncomeLoss, EPS, dedupes by period end, and emits 8 quarters
   of history with computed YoY% and per-row margins. Tagged source:
   'sec_edgar_xbrl_history'. OSS-style tickers (small caps) now get
   a populated 8-Quarter Margin & Surprise Trend table — surprise
   columns stay empty (no consensus to compare against) but the
   actual revenue / margin trajectory is real and rendered.

C. SECTOR KPI quote rendering — IndiaInstitutionalReport now shows
   the matching transcript sentence below the KPI description as
   '↳ "…"' italic green when a concall provided evidence. Hover
   on the status pill also surfaces the quote.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
